The paper discusses the generation of a safe fluent API, which is a topic related to programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The focus on the use of type parameters and the construction of a deterministic finite automaton (DFA) suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the mention of semantic constraints and the use of a DFA also suggests a connection to systems and control (cs.SY).
